{"tid":1626402,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聯合國人權事務高級專員籲 就香港示威召開獨立調查","createTime":"2019-10-05T11:04:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T11:54:03.000Z","uid":130626,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2a26efb40de849bda175d017bdda34c945d1d583","tid":1626402,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:04:28.000Z","msg":"香港「反送中」示威持續不斷，而且暴力程度更有升級之勢，聯合國人權事務高級專員巴切萊特（Michelle Bachelet）周六呼籲就涉及示威的暴力行為召開獨立調查，強調任何應對動亂的措施都必須基於法律。<br />\n<br />\n目前身在馬來西亞吉隆坡的巴切萊特表示，自香港爆發反政府示威後，兩名年青示威者先後遭警員開槍射傷，更有一名印尼女記者右眼被橡膠子彈擊中，證實永久失明。巴切萊特說︰「我們對涉及一些示威的嚴重暴力感到憂慮......亦對警員及示威者受傷，包括記者及示威者遭執法人員射擊感到困擾。」<br />\n<br />\n她認為香港政府應該盡快就所有暴力行為包括開槍事件，召開一個「有效、迅速、獨立及公正調查」，「我強烈譴責所有暴力行為，呼籲當局及所有抗爭者採取和平及非暴力形式」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191005/large/1570269440_6246.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191005%2Flarge%2F1570269440_6246.jpg&h=c16db703&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巴切萊特呼籲就香港反送中示威召開獨立調查<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191005/60121358\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191005%2F60121358&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk4hgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=0eb92843\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191005%2F60121358&h=c2876998\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191005/60121358</a>"},{"pid":"d00bf044c383859c2186e38b313beaa1da07e4f2","tid":1626402,"uid":261470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:05:06.000Z","msg":"助推"},{"pid":"f78879055baa86e01b9ebdab75b34bd294cd3b3a","tid":1626402,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:05:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"678cbcd1f3133d0b835c22b9e0bf1e27e36663aa","tid":1626402,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:09:27.000Z","msg":"【行動】商戶蝕大本對政府怨氣重！大家係時候出手connect沉默的中小企！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1625700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1625700</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n隨著政府不斷挑釁香港人，火上加油，導致抗爭越演越烈。<span style=\"color: red;\"> 反送中持續了一百多日，警察胡亂鎮壓，亂放催淚彈，對地區造成嘅滋擾，無人幫襯對佢地來講造成極大損失。<br />\n<strong>依家開始有唔少藍絲或扮中立嘅商人對政府及警察產生怨言。</strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請大家利用呢個機會，廣泛向商戶宣傳，爭取商戶棄暗投明，企起香港人一方，或至少唔再支持政府、警察，以及港共保皇黨。</span></strong><br />\n請推我個post以了解當中嘅行動策略。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1625700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1625700</a>"},{"pid":"c5ea44a51015d5dce3f9dcefb253c62b148b2a73","tid":1626402,"uid":7391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:14:30.000Z","msg":"雖然得把口，但好過無"},{"pid":"010d214edef00f2ac953a267957c2112afd98dd7","tid":1626402,"uid":270237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:17:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bh9mrsZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBh9mrsZ.jpg&h=4c2d1ca6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G6pp8Gn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG6pp8Gn.jpg&h=08881697&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b02c93fc4608b01b95d89f97eb2f4cc60f360ae","tid":1626402,"uid":94021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:41:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ccdacf5db72d825f2614c95bec90968050edf43","tid":1626402,"uid":256620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d00bf044c383859c2186e38b313beaa1da07e4f2","tid":1626402,"uid":261470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c